---
title: Rosemary Mustard Sirloin Steaks with Garlic Mashed Potatoes and Roasted Brussels Sprouts
description: Demi-glaze is an intensely rich, glossy sauce reduction. A master sauce of French cuisine, traditional demi-glace requires simmering beef stock for hours. But don’t panic---we’ve made it for you! When our own rich, glossy demi is used in the pan sauce for this luxurious dish, it creates a savory depth of flavor that’ll make anyone you feed believe you slaved at the stove for hours. Don’t worry, though--we’ll never tell.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rosemary-mustard-sirloin-steaks-330a78a9.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/rosemary-mustard-sirloin-steaks-5bef0e3930006c3a160c5522-44342a6a.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 40 minutes
author: HelloFresh
